list.name: Default
list.comment: Added the PredictorFactory and restructured the program main.

MESSAGE.value: Implemented StockMetric class to connect metrics to stocks and quotes.
Changed the data structure. Instead of using quotes with metrics we now use metric lists in stocks.
Added some more simple predictors with accuracy evaluations. Logisitc regression seems best with about 54%.
Added AdjustedCloseMetric. Fixed minor typos and bugs.
Added parameter for NQuere size in predictors.
Made NQuote and Quote immuatable. NQuote now contains all Quotes useful for computing certain metrics. YahooStockLoader now fetches the name of the stock.
Fixed a problem when NQuotes are created. They should now end correctly but may be "truncated" in the start.
Added the new Settings file using Gson.
Added the PredictorFactory and restructured the program main.
